I"<p>The industry career path can be incredibly rewarding, challenging, and fun, but how do we get started? How do we break into industry after graduating with our PhD or completing our postdoc? Making the move to industry can sometimes be a challenge, and this question of <strong>how</strong> is a big one. In this blog post we will build off of our previous post (<a href="http://microbiology.github.io/blog/pivot-careers/">career trajectory within industry</a>) and discuss some ways to get started with pursuing a career in industry.</p>
